headline: Bitcoin Price Nears $108,000. Crypto Bulls See It Jumping This High.
summary: Bitcoin has hit yet another record high.  Thank President-elect Donald Trump and his crypto friendly rhetoric for fueling the rally.  Bitcoin  is up 2.3% over the last 24 hours to last trade at $107,017, according to CoinDesk data.
